🎓 45 Days Professional Makeup Course – Full Details

📅 Duration: 45 Days
⏰ Timings: 5 hours/day (Flexible morning & afternoon batches)
🏫 Mode: Offline (In academy) / Online (if available)

⸻

✨ What You Will Learn:

🔸 Week 1: Basics of Makeup & Skin Prep
	•	Skin analysis & skin types
	•	CTM (Cleanse, Tone, Moisturize)
	•	Primer & color correction theory
	•	Understanding face shapes & undertones

🔸 Week 2: Foundation & Base Perfection
	•	Foundation application (liquid, cream, stick)
	•	Concealing & highlighting
	•	Compact & setting techniques
	•	Contour & blush placement

🔸 Week 3: Eye Makeup Techniques
	•	Eyebrow shaping & filling
	•	Day & evening eye makeup
	•	Glitter & cut crease
	•	Smokey eyes & eyeliner styles

🔸 Week 4: Bridal Makeup Special
	•	North Indian Bridal Look
	•	South Indian Bridal Look
	•	Haldi, Mehendi, Reception looks
	•	Saree & dupatta draping styles

🔸 Week 5: Advanced Techniques
	•	HD makeup
	•	Airbrush makeup (Introductory)
	•	International makeup look
	•	Creative/editorial looks

🔸 Week 6: Portfolio & Business Skills
	•	Building client confidence
	•	Bridal consultation practice
	•	Social media makeup marketing
	•	Final photoshoot for portfolio

⸻

🎁 Bonus Inclusions:
	•	Free Makeup Vanity Kit (optional add-on)
	•	Brush handling & hygiene training
	•	Certification on course completion
	•	100% practical + theory classes
	•	Lifetime support & guidance

⸻

📸 Who Is This Course For?
	•	Aspiring makeup artists
	•	Salon professionals wanting to upskill
	•	Freelancers & bridal makeup artists
	•	Content creators/beauty influencers
